    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >停下，转弯，冲过去！一次碰撞就出局的指令游戏！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/481688b7355ef3d71453dac6d02e5171.avif?t=1756879125\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pocket＆Zooom是什么游戏？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pocket &amp; Zooom是一个通过指挥飞机到达终点的益智游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以发出的指令总共只有6种。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看似简单其实又很困难・・・</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让我们制定策略，让所有飞机到达终点！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pocket＆Zooom游戏的玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[时刻观察机场！]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >飞机会朝着目标前进，但如果不加注意，很容易与其他飞机或障碍物碰撞。要仔细观察机场，尽早发现靠近危险的飞机并采取措施。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/71f8932c31a0952b9257bfafc0efecaf.poster.avif?t=1756879125\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/71f8932c31a0952b9257bfafc0efecaf.webm?t=1756879125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/71f8932c31a0952b9257bfafc0efecaf.mp4?t=1756879125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[来发出指令吧！]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了使飞机远离危险，我们使用“指令卡”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从“停止”、“改变航线”等6张卡片中选择合适的卡牌，引导飞机到达目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/fc4d48e5fe31b4f2a24dd613db9f8ec8.poster.avif?t=1756879125\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/fc4d48e5fe31b4f2a24dd613db9f8ec8.webm?t=1756879125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/fc4d48e5fe31b4f2a24dd613db9f8ec8.mp4?t=1756879125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[注意不要过度使用卡牌！]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用卡牌后会产生冷却时间，重新使用需要时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要仔细考虑使用的时机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/5362b5ec1da34a7df64d705068f28353.poster.avif?t=1756879125\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/5362b5ec1da34a7df64d705068f28353.webm?t=1756879125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/5362b5ec1da34a7df64d705068f28353.mp4?t=1756879125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[诱导所有飞机到达终点！]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >安全地避开各种危险，让飞机到达终点就可以成功通关成功！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是，引导的飞机不止一架。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着关卡的增加，引导的飞机数量也会增多，危险也会随之增加。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引导所有飞机到达终点，实现通关吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/3dbb982baeacbeade624d2e3b4f89539.poster.avif?t=1756879125\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/3dbb982baeacbeade624d2e3b4f89539.webm?t=1756879125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453680/extras/3dbb982baeacbeade624d2e3b4f89539.mp4?t=1756879125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
